strings: <voice_0x01001617><se_def>Angelo: Why did you come here, Marcello?

<voice_0x01001618><se_def>Marcello: To settle a score.
Nothing more.

<voice_0x01001619><se_def>Marcello: You could have died in a ditch
for all I cared, little brother.
But not before my debt was repaid.
<voice_0x0100161A><se_def>Marcello: It makes no difference to me whether you people live or die.
<voice_0x01001621><se_def>Marcello: So give him a message from me: we're even.
